caption.p: mRNA levels of IFN-γ, IL-6, IL-10, TNF-α, IL-2, and IL-4 quantified using real-time PCR in the brains ( A) and spleens ( B) of AG129 mice at 2 days after subcutaneous infection with 10 2 PFU of M-30 and S-27 CHIKV strains. The asterisks show significant differences by the Kruskal–Wallis test (*) and by the Mann–Whitney U-test (**), P < 0.05.
